  "instructions": [
    "Heat the cataplana vessel over medium heat and add the cubed pork shoulder.",
    "Cook the pork until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onions to the cataplana and cook until they are translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the fermented cabbage, caraway seeds, salt, and black pepper to the cataplana.",
    "Pour in the chicken broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer the stew for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the sour cream and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh dill."
